          <h1>Security</h1>
          
          <p>At lnksbot, the security of your data is our top priority. We employ industry-standard security measures to protect your information and ensure the integrity of our service.</p>
          
          <h2>Data Protection</h2>
          <p>We implement multiple layers of security to protect your data:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Encryption:</strong> All data transmitted between your device and our servers is encrypted using TLS/SSL protocols. Your stored data is also encrypted at rest.</li>
            <li><strong>Secure Infrastructure:</strong> Our services are hosted on secure cloud infrastructure with advanced security features, including firewalls, intrusion detection, and regular security audits.</li>
            <li><strong>Access Controls:</strong> We maintain strict access controls to ensure that only authorized personnel can access our systems and your data.</li>
            <li><strong>Regular Backups:</strong> We perform regular backups of all data to prevent loss in case of system failures.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2>Account Security</h2>
          <p>We provide several features to help you keep your account secure:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Strong Password Requirements:</strong> We enforce the use of strong passwords to protect your account.</li>
            <li><strong>Two-Factor Authentication (2FA):</strong> We offer 2FA as an additional layer of security for your account.</li>
            <li><strong>Session Management:</strong> You can view and manage all active sessions and log out remotely if needed.</li>
            <li><strong>Security Notifications:</strong> We'll notify you of any suspicious activity or important security events related to your account.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2>Content Security</h2>
          <p>When you save links to our service, we take steps to ensure the security of your content:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Secure Processing:</strong> All content processing is done in secure environments with strict access controls.</li>
            <li><strong>Malware Scanning:</strong> We scan all links for potential security threats before processing them.</li>
            <li><strong>Isolated Storage:</strong> Your content is stored in isolated environments to prevent unauthorized access.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2>Security Practices</h2>
          <p>Our security practices include:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Regular Security Audits:</strong> We conduct regular security audits and vulnerability assessments of our systems.</li>
            <li><strong>Penetration Testing:</strong> We perform penetration testing to identify and address potential security vulnerabilities.</li>
            <li><strong>Security Training:</strong> Our team undergoes regular security training to stay up-to-date with the latest security best practices.</li>
            <li><strong>Incident Response:</strong> We have a comprehensive incident response plan in place to address security incidents quickly and effectively.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2>Reporting Security Issues</h2>
          <p>If you discover a security vulnerability or have concerns about the security of our service, please contact us immediately at security@lnksbot.com. We take all security reports seriously and will investigate promptly.</p>
          
          <h2>Security Updates</h2>
          <p>We continuously monitor for security threats and update our systems regularly to address potential vulnerabilities. We also keep our dependencies and third-party libraries up-to-date to ensure we're protected against known security issues.</p>
          
